              <p>It is considered the subject that is more focused on creating a long-lasting user experience. It is more about understanding the hidden emotions that play an important role to influence people’s behavior and decision-making, and then catalyzing the action on that information to design compelling user interactions making a rational decision, based on real evidence. This past design element has 5 major elements that enable the designer to create a masterpiece that triggers the consumer's purchase decisions.</p>
